"8WRGAC36.1A1G" and "1520" is silkscreened on the main board.
===Specifications=== * D-Link DIR-890L/R Wireless AC3200 Tri-Band Gigabit Cloud Router * Simultaneous Tri-Band: deliver faster Wi-Fi speeds of up to 3200Mpbs :(600Mbps on 2.4GHz + 1300Mbps + 1300Mbps on 5GHz)
